Class ClearanceMatrix

java.lang.Object
eu.mihosoft.freerouting.rules.ClearanceMatrix
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ClearanceMatrix extends Object implements Serializable
NxN Matrix describing the spacing restrictions between N clearance classes on a fixed set of layers.
